<p>The current version of NewsGator always sends HTML to the posting plug-ins, even if you compose in plain text.  We're planning to offer an option for plain text in a future version. One option for now would be to create a "shim" plug-in which would use a regex to strip the HTML tags...not pretty, but it would work.</p>
